{"expireTime":9007200851393017000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-ast-f05053b3d3062d4855aef45ae6aa9823-gatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-responsive-iframegatsby-remark-prismjsgatsby-remark-copy-linked-filesgatsby-remark-smartypants-","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"I’m incredibly excited as I write this blog and mark the start of my blogging journey.","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":87,"offset":87},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":87,"offset":87},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"In the past few months, people around the world have suffered tremendous losses.","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":89},"end":{"line":4,"column":81,"offset":169},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":89},"end":{"line":4,"column":81,"offset":169},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"As I write this blogpost, COVID19 is raging across the globe, numerous places in India are experiencing extreme weather conditions, Beirut has witnessed a 2700+ ton Ammonium Nitrate explosion and the Apple Fire has forced thousands to flee in California. Safe to say, 2020 has not been kind to anyone.","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":171},"end":{"line":6,"column":302,"offset":472},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":171},"end":{"line":6,"column":302,"offset":472},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"However, the past few months of staying at home and college campus shutdown have given me lots of opportunities to learn and expirement with different tools and technologies. I have been able to widen my skills and tinker with lots of new ideas and concepts and I am very grateful and thankful for all these opportunities I have got.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":474},"end":{"line":8,"column":334,"offset":807},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":474},"end":{"line":8,"column":334,"offset":807},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Over the past few months of diving into web development, app development, designing user experiences and even some data analysis and machine learning, I have realised the importance of documenting one’s journey. Having a blog will allow me to keep a track of my progress, share my thoughts and ideas and learn to communicate them better.","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":809},"end":{"line":10,"column":338,"offset":1146},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":809},"end":{"line":10,"column":338,"offset":1146},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"I am excited to share a piece of my mind with the internet and look forward to writing regularly!","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":1148},"end":{"line":12,"column":98,"offset":1245},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":1148},"end":{"line":12,"column":98,"offset":1245},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"html","title":null,"url":"./hello_world.jpg","alt":"Hello World","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1247},"end":{"line":14,"column":34,"offset":1280},"indent":[]},"value":"<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2234a32cafd696bfcac3b8d50c288d7f/eea4a/hello_world.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'